descriptionHtml:
I felt that the moon needed a bit more, comical look. So I chose to go with the female reproductive system in place of Masser. (Just a diagram of system). Just place the \"Sky\" folder in the \"Textures\" folder and you\'re set to go. This is just for mere comical(and boredom) purposes. Hope you enjoy! 

For people who don\'t know how to get to their data folder: C:Drive>Program Files(x86)>steam>steamapps>common>Skyrim>Data>Drop sky file into textures folder.
author: SPARTAN NICK004
